    <title>Hexo_Next博客安装及配置</title>
    <url>/2020/03/20/Hexo-Next%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85%E5%8F%8A%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<h1 id="安装"><a href="#安装" class="headerlink" title="安装"></a>安装</h1><h2 id="依赖安装"><a href="#依赖安装" class="headerlink" title="依赖安装"></a>依赖安装</h2><ul>
<li><a href="https://git-scm.com/downloads" target="_blank" rel="noopener">git</a> </li>
<li><a href="https://nodejs.org/en/download/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">node.js</a> <h2 id="安装hexo"><a href="#安装hexo" class="headerlink" title="安装hexo"></a>安装hexo</h2></li>
</ul>
<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm install -g hexo-cli</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h2 id="生成博客系统"><a href="#生成博客系统" class="headerlink" title="生成博客系统"></a>生成博客系统</h2><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo init &lt;folder&gt;</span><br><span class="line">cd &lt;folder&gt;</span><br><span class="line">npm install</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<blockquote>
<p>hexo常用命令</p>
</blockquote>
<h2 id="部署"><a href="#部署" class="headerlink" title="部署"></a>部署</h2><h3 id="命令式简单快速的方法"><a href="#命令式简单快速的方法" class="headerlink" title="命令式简单快速的方法"></a>命令式简单快速的方法</h3><ul>
<li>登录github，创建 <username>.github.io 仓库</li>
<li>编辑站点配置文件 <code>_config.yml</code> ，编辑后内容如下<figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># Deployment</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">## Docs: https://hexo.io/docs/deployment.html</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">deploy:</span> </span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">    type:</span> <span class="string">git</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">    repo:</span> <span class="attr">https://github.com/&lt;user_name&gt;/&lt;user_name&gt;.github.io</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">    branch:</span> <span class="string">&lt;branch&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li>
<li>用hexo命令一键发布<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo deploy</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

</li>
</ul>
<a id="more"></a>


<h1 id="简单配置"><a href="#简单配置" class="headerlink" title="简单配置"></a>简单配置</h1><h1 id="主题配置"><a href="#主题配置" class="headerlink" title="主题配置"></a>主题配置</h1>]]></content>
